# IEOR_Individual_project_UmmeHani
Medical Diagnosis — use Bayes to predict if a patient has a disease based on symptoms. Very classic Bayes example — like "given fever + cough, what's P(flu)?" Great for showing the theorem in a non-CS context.
Weather Prediction — given today's weather features, predict tomorrow (rainy/sunny). Uses conditional probability tables, very visual and intuitive.
Credit Card Fraud Detection — classify transactions as fraud or genuine based on amount, time, location patterns. Very real-world and impactful.
